And by the way:`,mdx("blockquote",{parentName:"li"},mdx("blockquote",{parentName:"blockquote"},mdx("p",{parentName:"blockquote"},"This kind of educational non-fiction writing has everything standup has, except it's much easier, and feels more valuable. Its just as engaging and has enough jokes, but doesnt have to be laugh out loud funny, just fun to read, and it can teach people things."))))),mdx("p",null,"concrete examples"),mdx("p",null,"Action Checklisr"),mdx("ul",null,mdx("li",{parentName:"ul"},"Add jokes")))}MDXContent.isMDXComponent=!0;
